    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >关于 &quot;特工&quot;礼包</h2><br>该武器系列中有家喻户晓的武器并第一无二武器迷彩，都有万圣节特殊设计。这些武器的魔法气氛的外观一定会引起大家的注意。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1753570/extras/eb5b842303e6a62ba36abf46f6463b99.poster.avif?t=1685626283\" width=616 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1753570/extras/eb5b842303e6a62ba36abf46f6463b99.webm?t=1685626283\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1753570/extras/eb5b842303e6a62ba36abf46f6463b99.mp4?t=1685626283\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>武器套中有六把强大的武器，一定会增加你的战斗力量。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1753570/extras/5bea4a131945f99eeb255087e559b103.poster.avif?t=1685626283\" width=616 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1753570/extras/5bea4a131945f99eeb255087e559b103.webm?t=1685626283\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1753570/extras/5bea4a131945f99eeb255087e559b103.mp4?t=1685626283\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Stoner LMG A1 &quot;Poltergeist&quot;</h2>斯通纳 LMG 是一款由奈特军械公司生产的轻机枪，也是美国著名枪械设计师尤金·斯通纳最后参与的设计项目之一。 此外，Stoner LMG A1跟其他武器对比的话，换弹速度比较高 - 4秒钟是一种很短时间，是吧。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1753570/extras/b30a6d0c57d936eb0b55b9f7225dfb0c.avif?t=1685626283\" width=616 height=256 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Marlin 1894 Custom &quot;Poltergeist&quot;</h2>Marlin 1894 Custom距离和精度超级好 - 瞄准时和腰射时，都很好。在近战的时候Marlin武器如果不能一射就击杀敌人，那就能够推到敌人。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1753570/extras/395e059ba049d0b54b91ce354cb6ceca.avif?t=1685626283\" width=616 height=256 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >SIG MPX SBR Custom &quot;Poltergeist&quot;</h2>SIG MPX SBR Custom 是一款冲锋枪，采用非常规设计，实现无与伦比的性能。它将使用者的安全性提升到了一个新的水平，并具有很高的战场适应性以及在最残酷的环境下久经考验的可靠性，开创了一个全新的冲锋枪类别。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1753570/extras/f2a33aca2fcd8fb552efc024c1009829.avif?t=1685626283\" width=616 height=256 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Bushmaster BA50 &quot;Poltergeist&quot;</h2>这是是一把栓动式弹匣供弹步枪，使用 .50 BMG 弹药。这种狙击步枪几乎可以做到枪枪必杀。即使相隔很远，武装到牙齿的敌人也无法在这种武器的枪口下幸免。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1753570/extras/5883399af01e7fee22639e58ebf3425b.avif?t=1685626283\" width=616 height=256 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Maxim 9 &quot;Poltergeist&quot;</h2>Maxim 9 是世界上首款内置抑制器的 9 毫米手枪，可腰射，并在PvP中使用任何口径弹药时均可保护听力。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1753570/extras/5a0c1bca02f3d564770559f3480e0155.avif?t=1685626283\" width=616 height=256 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >蝴蝶刀 &quot;Poltergeist&quot;</h2>蝴蝶刀是一种小折刀。它的特点是两个刀柄沿着柄脚反转，当合上时，刀刃会隐藏在刀柄上的凹槽内。蝴蝶刀是一种优秀近战武器，使用它的玩家可以用它来一下子就杀死任何敌人，背心也不是一种可靠的护甲。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1753570/extras/0d65a6a79390fe41ee0d2b6ccae8b761.avif?t=1685626283\" width=616 height=256 /></span><br><br>当然，玩家可以通过使用这些武器来争取多样的成就。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1753570/extras/d2238b0f227b80b48f9dc68d236753d7.avif?t=1685626283\" width=616 height=256 /></span><br><br>支付好之后请稍等15分钟左右。如果物品还没到账的话，请重新启动游戏。",
